{"type": "article", "id": 44319, "title": "混凝土做的咖啡机，是电器也是一个艺术品｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-08-21T23:12:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 26039, "name": "Seletti"}, {"id": 6996, "name": "Studio Job"}, {"id": 43392, "name": "Montaag"}, {"id": 43393, "name": "Viktor Hertz"}, {"id": 43394, "name": "Éric Nado"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 128, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170821192347P7jGJrfzVeYx3K2E.png", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>AnZa by Montaag Products LLC</h3><p>2014 年，美国加州设计公司 <a href=\"http://montaag.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Montaag</a> 的成员们提出了一个想法：有没有可能在不牺牲功能的情况下，设计一件像是艺术品的电器？基于对咖啡的热爱，他们很快就决定拿咖啡机作为突破口进行一场设计实验，并于近日公布了这款与咖啡机修理店 <a href=\"http://www.kanencoffee.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kanen Coffee</a> 联手打造的咖啡机 AnZa。它最大的特点在于使用了不常见于咖啡机的材料，例如混凝土、可丽耐、黄铜以及木材等等，看起来就像是一件漂亮的雕塑。目前，两种材质的咖啡机正在 Kickstarter 上开展<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/montaagproducts/anza-redefining-the-espresso-machine-in-concrete-a\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹</a>，售价从 749 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821192118N2MOpSTJXlKYGaxE.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821192118vwx8JbK1E2jThB6m.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821192118IQwCtArHp1JvXx8c.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.661765\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>UN_LIMITED EDITIONS by Seletti &amp; Studio Job</h3><p>在即将于 9 月举行的巴黎家居装饰博览会（Maison &amp; Objet）上，擅长将稀奇古怪的生活和艺术元素与产品结合的意大利家居品牌 <a href=\"http://www.seletti.it/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Seletti</a> 将带来与设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.studiojob.be/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Studio Job</a> 的首个合作系列 UN_LIMITED EDITIONS。Studio Job 此前就出品过不少古灵精怪的产品，他们这次挑选了美式餐饮文化中经典的汉堡和热狗形象，让沙发也能挑动食欲。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821192054V5IBvkPoX3eKbJuT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.726161\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821192054jWQ5o0b7AukaRvrh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.695599\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821192054iU4OTPmW9uw3exnG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.803178\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821192054ut6TaPB2NIS9FREM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.848411\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Pictogram music posters by Viktor Hertz</h3><p>说起把音乐里的梗作为灵感的设计，你或许会想起那个曾带来<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/37525.html\">歌名地图</a>和<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/41218.html\">摇滚动物园</a>的英国设计工作室 Dorothy。今天介绍的瑞典平面设计师 <a href=\"http://viktorhertz.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Viktor Hertz</a> 同样热衷于将流行文化转变成创意，在始于 2011 年的首个个人项目 Pictogram music posters 中，他尝试用简单的图案揭示歌名中的内涵。如果你喜欢这种风格，可以通过作品的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/48273653/Pictogram-music-posters-2017\" rel=\"nofollow\">Behance</a> 页面找到购买方式。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821192042WD3pzjxECAQiFL4Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821192042KpEi2PWzueLl5STx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821192042me3zAiLDnRCXMPQ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821192043byW2iAknqCeIRBMm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821192043NHlXSMPGp04FzxuY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>My Concrete City by Margherita Abi Hanna</h3><p>2010 年，黎巴嫩设计师 Margherita Abi Hanna 在结束米兰的硕士学位后回到了家乡贝鲁特，并于同年成立了以设计首饰为主的个人工作室。在见证了不少历史建筑遭遇拆迁之后，她决定通过设计向它们致敬。在最新的 My Concrete City 系列中，她挑选了历史建筑中比较著名的细节，将它们制作成指环或是项链挂坠。如果你感兴趣的话，可以在她的<a href=\"http://www.bymargherita.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">个人网站</a>上找到购买方式。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821192023Lcw2UdueTKYtDxsN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708211920237U0sAG4WfZPvXoxc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708211920244cMNIak6d7fp8J2C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821192023EW4dA2a3lPNDoeCF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821192024v1zM3ay5HrqumUxD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Float by iAN Yen</h3><p>基于庄子的“其生若浮”，台湾设计师 <a href=\"http://www.designyxr.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">iAN Yen</a> 尝试将山水画的意境与产品设计融合，打造了这套名为浮器的概念茶器。整套茶器由一壶二盏构成，涟漪状的底座与壶盖不仅优雅，还能起到散热作用。从侧面看，壶柄构成的弧度还有一种湖上明月的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821191958xcaho502jik1nKgw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708211919592rMdAIZR4XqHpgTb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663814\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708211919591jkEQncb5SNlhsFG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708211919584nKtYbjrd9ImZo3z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.443765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821191958oe2BJajsrlm1WK0S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.696822\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Typewriter Guns by Éric Nado</h3><p>语言也是武器的一种，不断地改变着历史的走向。这套名为 Typewriter Guns 的模型是由加拿大艺术家 <a href=\"http://ericnado.com/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Éric Nado</a> 自 2012 年起开展的艺术项目，他以老式打字机 Olivetti Lettera 32 作为素材，将它们拆解后重组为把文字作为子弹的机枪。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708211923029WzNgHD6Z8OmctYf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.503671\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821192302v6PewMyVg501r4zk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665163\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821192302IRv1OGQZVD726qMx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.822034\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170821192303FRQCPWmLGdYE9uZx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665039\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}